Yao Q, Zhu L, Shi Z, Banerjee S, Chen C. Topoisomerase-modulated genome-wide DNA supercoiling domains colocalize with nuclear compartments and regulate human gene expression. Nat Struct Mol Biol. Published online August 16, 2024. doi:10.1038/s41594-024-01377-5
